<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.4.4">
<l>ilaṅkaiceṟ ṟavaṉē yeṉṉumpiṉṉum</l>
<l>valaṅkoḷ puḷḷuyarttā yeṉṉumuḷḷa</l>
<l>malaṅkavev vuyirkkuṅ kaṇṇīrmikak</l>
<l>kalaṅkik kaitoḻu niṉṟivaḷē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You who subdued Laṅkā, she says. [Then] again,</l>
<l>you who is elevated on the strong bird, she says. She sighs</l>
<l>hotly while [her] mind is confused. While tears well up</l>
<l>this one stirs [and] folds [her] hands in worship, constantly.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
